<plot>A Sustainable Galapagos? analyzes the state of the popular archipelago tourist destination off the coast of Ecuador. Through interviews with a cross-section of residents, tour guides, volunteers, and employees of environmental organizations, the film uncovers problems, solutions, and the future of the Galapagos Islands.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?016769</url></doc>
